      2           * @file
      3           * @brief       Low-Level Input for the Melexis MLX90621 16x4 infrared array sensor.
      4           *
      5           * @details     This LLI initializes and reads the MLX90621 16x4 infrared array sensor.
      6           *              For details of the implementation, refer to the MLX90621 data sheet.
      7           *
      8           *              This LLI performs the following actions:
      9           *                  - Read LLI configuration from the setting file
     10           *                  - Initialization of the MLX90621
     11           *                  - Read the MLX90621 EEPROM data
     12           *                  - Write oscillator trimming value
     13           *                  - Write device configuration value
     14           *                  - Read the raw (uncompensated) 16x4 infrared array data
     15           *
